The Cubana deluxe costs 50,000
The Sofa Cubana costs 30,000 each
The classic and deluxe cubana comes with LED lantan, candy, peanut and cookies 

We also have a Vip 20 seater lounge (10% discount on food and drinks)

Rooms: We have 3 different room types:

